        CORV E 6 
        CORV EEE 2
        CORV EEE 3
        CORV E 6
		CORV E  0 A_TakeInventory("CorvusShootCloneTrigger",1,0,AAPTR_Master)
		Goto See
	Pain:
		CORV G 3
		CORV G 3 A_Pain
		Goto See
